OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772118239
OL,3,CWoman arrested over Brit's 'murder' in
OL,4,CTenerife hotel
OL,6,FA 56-year-old woman has been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of murder after the death
OL,8,Fof a British holidaymaker in Tenerife.
OL,10,FRussell Watts, 63, from Rotherham, was
OL,11,Ffound dead in his room at the Hotel
OL,12,FCatalonia Punta Del Rey in the
OL,13,FCandelaria area of the Spanish island
OL,14,Fon Saturday, 10 January.
OL,16,FSouth Yorkshire Police said a woman
OL,17,Ffrom the Rotherham area was arrested
OL,18,Fon Wednesday, 25 February, on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
