PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772118239
OL,3,CWoman arrested over Brit's 'murder' in
OL,4,CTenerife hotel
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Ben Wood said: "This is a
OL,7,Fcomplex case and our thoughts first
OL,8,Fand foremost remain with Russell's
OL,9,Ffamily, friends and loved ones.
OL,11,F"Our investigation into Russell's
OL,12,Fdeath is still at an early stage and
OL,13,Fwe are carrying out a number of
OL,14,Fextensive enquiries to piece together
OL,15,Fthe events which led to Russell's
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,F"We are really keen to hear from
OL,19,Fanyone who was staying in the hotel
OL,20,Faround the time of Russell's death."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
