PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1772118239
OL,3,CWoman arrested over Brit's 'murder' in
OL,4,CTenerife hotel
OL,6,FHe urged anyone who "saw something
OL,7,Fsuspicious" or had "relevant
OL,8,Finformation" to report it.
OL,10,F"Even the smallest piece of
OL,11,Finformation could prove crucial and I
OL,12,Fwould implore anyone who may know
OL,13,Fsomething to get in contact with us
OL,14,Fimmediately," he added.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
